  "records": {
    "description": "Storage input system based of PI002 which has built in item preprocessing. Has main and bulk inputs; loose items are loaded by a CUD loader; bulk input uses an IsFull so it only outputs full boxes",
    "features": [
      "Starts from noteblock",
      "Pauseable",
      "Fully hopperlocked (except CUD loader empty box distribution hopper, which should be locked externally)",
      "CUD loader for loose items",
      "Very small (7x10x6)",
      "Good UI"
    ]
